content.problemStatement:
Jason is writing a program to count down from 30 to 25 using a while loop, but the program runs indefinitely.

```c
#include

int main() {
    int count = 30;
    while (count > 25) {
        printf("%d\n", count);
    }
    return 0;
}
````
---

**Expected output:**
```default
30
29
28
27
26
````

